2020-07-09 07:15:43.174 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (60ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']

IF EXISTS
    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

) AS [t] ON [d].[CategoriesId] = [t].[Id]

    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AvgPrice], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]

SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight], [t].[Id], [t].[Code], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[IngredientId], [t1].[CompanyId], [t1].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t] ON [d].[CategoriesId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AvgPrice], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]

    ) AS [t0] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t1] ON [d].[Id] = [t1].[DishId]
WHERE [d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0
ORDER BY [d].[Id], [t].[Id], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[IngredientId], [t1].[Id]

IF EXISTS
    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0

SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight], [t].[Id], [t].[Code], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[IngredientId], [t1].[CompanyId], [t1].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t] ON [d].[CategoriesId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AvgPrice], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t0] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t1] ON [d].[Id] = [t1].[DishId]
WHERE [d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0
ORDER BY [d].[Id], [t].[Id], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[IngredientId], [t1].[Id]

2020-07-09 16:47:58.371 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__ef_filter__CompanyId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']

2020-07-09 16:47:58.635 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (35ms) [Parameters=[@__ef_filter__CompanyId_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3='?' (DbType = Int32), @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight], [t].[Id], [t].[Code], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[IngredientId], [t1].[CompanyId], [t1].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t] ON [d].[CategoriesId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AvgPrice], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t0] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t1] ON [d].[Id] = [t1].[DishId]
